title: Barrera vs Morales I
description:
Barrera vs. Morales I

The bout took place on February 19, 2000, at the Mandalay Bay Resort and Casino, in Las Vegas and was televised on HBO Boxing. Morales was declared winner by split decision, with scores of 115-112, 114-113 and 113-114 and captured the WBO Super Bantamweight title. This bout was named as Ring Magazine's Fight of the Year for 2000, before being named as the best Fight of all time in the same year.
